## Plan Review — Adaptive Dispatch (FAST/LITE/FULL)

After writing `plan.md`, compute escalation:

```bash
harness escalation-score compute --phase plan --deliverables N --estimated-files N [--security] [--schema] [--api] [--review-score X] --json
```

**Score >= {{ gate_full_review_min }} → FULL**: all 5 roles, strict synthesis. **Score {{ gate_summary_confirm_min }}–{{ (gate_full_review_min | int) - 1 }} → LITE**: all 5 roles, lenient synthesis (accept WARN as advisory). **Score < {{ gate_summary_confirm_min }} → FAST**: skip review, save fast-pass eval:
```bash
harness save-eval --kind plan --task task-NNN --verdict PASS --score {{ pass_threshold }} --body "Plan auto-approved (FAST, escalation score N)"
```

